{"tid":781063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［正能量］一人一個為自己感到驕傲自豪嘅事蹟","createTime":"2018-08-15T15:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T15:21:24.000Z","uid":143427,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"88a0403791c658cf05667ed25716e7da94aed3f3","tid":781063,"uid":143427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:08:36.000Z","msg":"從未捐過錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岀街賣旗個啲唔洗講啦<br />\n仲記得小學個陣班房成日轉個紫色羊要我地捐錢，好多小學雞都會妹下妹下放5蚊10蚊落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我當時已經覺得智障，心諗有錢捐俾我唔好<br />\n<br />\n真心為自己感到驕傲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/230516_5de265ec63d192ffa3077bdd8ba74ef5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F230516_5de265ec63d192ffa3077bdd8ba74ef5.png&h=fd5220c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係呢隻濕鳩羊，唔知呃咗幾多小學雞嘅錢，但唔洗旨意係我身上攞到一毫子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75bbe0fbddef95029445d048d0b235f4d0b236a","tid":781063,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:11:37.000Z","msg":"睇黎你人生都無乜野值得驕傲自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32c79466aaffa1f053d698a02b96900ea22994c","tid":781063,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"人地想問嘢嗰陣我即刻答到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1942b14fb40b98c02c171468ed59c2ea7f5892cf","tid":781063,"uid":143427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d75bbe0fbddef95029445d048d0b235f4d0b236a","tid":781063,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:11:37.000Z","msg":"睇黎你人生都無乜野值得驕傲自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:13:41.000Z","msg":"唔好打擊我好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b306e4a6c0aa06a4926631b8eaa1c7f09b2cac16","tid":781063,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:15:02.000Z","msg":"恥笑樓主條傻鳩"},{"pid":"1faa899fc4dd5aa49d71450f23dfe8638332d94c","tid":781063,"uid":143427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b306e4a6c0aa06a4926631b8eaa1c7f09b2cac16","tid":781063,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:15:02.000Z","msg":"恥笑樓主條傻鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a070b39a6a95291d73349532acd84abedf5d9814","tid":781063,"uid":143427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d11428150d32ae445423447b4f6b2eabdac3d6","tid":781063,"uid":143427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T13:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb2b7a0cb5bd65209581bad444290b3da5127cd","tid":781063,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:03:58.000Z","msg":"仲未自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ec09c2cd8339b83d17f3dcc357911c2fac791c","tid":781063,"uid":75870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:59:15.000Z","msg":"30年處子之身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186db5b7ecc354ce64aed5d6ee0fda2fec30edb2","tid":781063,"uid":143427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88ec09c2cd8339b83d17f3dcc357911c2fac791c","tid":781063,"uid":75870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:59:15